attributes.description: Timex Group India Limited is a group company of Tanager Group B.V. (formerly known as Timex Group B.V.). The Co is engaged in manufacturing and trading of watches and rendering of related after sales service. The Company also provides information and technology support services to the Group Companies. [1][2]
